&lt;li&gt;Handle new client inquiries and leads — turning warm introductions into long-term relationships&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Prospect for new clients through referrals, community engagement, and professional networks&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Leverage Farther&#39;s technology and planning tools to deliver a high-quality, personalized client experience&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Contribute to team operations and support internal succession planning as the practice grows&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
