&lt;li&gt;2+ years of experience in financial planning or wealth management&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong foundation in financial planning concepts — retirement, investment management, tax basics&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Relationship-first mindset with genuine care for clients&#39; long-term outcomes&lt;/li&gt;
